# Day Three: Today is all about conditional statements such as  if, elif, else and more!!
# Written By: Nick Phelps
# Date: May 07, 2024

# In today's project, we will be building a text based treasure hunt game. This project
# is intended to reinforce the learning we did today about conditional statements.
#
# To play the game, users will be prompted to input specific information based on a
# given prompt such as "You stand at a crossroad, do you want to go left or right?"
# The user would be expected to enter either "left" or "right".
#
# Please note that this code is not expected to include error handling such as
# input validation. If a user enters something that is not "left" or "right"
# then a message stating that the entered an invalid choice is displayed.

print('''
_                                     _     _                 _ 
| |                                   (_)   | |               | |
| |_ _ __ ___  __ _ ___ _   _ _ __ ___ _ ___| | __ _ _ __   __| |
| __| '__/ _ \/ _` / __| | | | '__/ _ \ / __| |/ _` | '_ \ / _` |
| |_| | |  __/ (_| \__ \ |_| | | |  __/ \__ \ | (_| | | | | (_| |
 \__|_|  \___|\__,_|___/\__,_|_|  \___|_|___/_|\__,_|_| |_|\__,_|
 ''')

print('''
*******************************************************************************
          |                   |                  |                     |
 _________|________________.=""_;=.______________|_____________________|_______
|                   |  ,-"_,=""     `"=.|                  |
|___________________|__"=._o`"-._        `"=.______________|___________________
          |                `"=._o`"=._      _`"=._                     |
 _________|_____________________:=._o "=._."_.-="'"=.__________________|_______
|                   |    __.--" , ; `"=._o." ,-"""-._ ".   |
|___________________|_._"  ,. .` ` `` ,  `"-._"-._   ". '__|___________________
          |           |o`"=._` , "` `; .". ,  "-._"-._; ;              |
 _________|___________| ;`-.o`"=._; ." ` '`."\` . "-._ /_______________|_______
|                   | |o;    `"-.o`"=._``  '` " ,__.--o;   |
|___________________|_| ;     (#) `-.o `"=.`_.--"_o.-; ;___|___________________
